0.title: Celebrity Special for SU2C 2018
0.plot: Joey Essex, Melinda Messenger, Sandra Martin from Gogglebox (2013) and Lady Colin Campbell bravely embark on blind dates with unsuspecting members of the public, in this special episode for Stand Up To Cancer.

1.title: Episode #11.1
1.plot: Septuagenarian Deanna has her first date in 20 years. Will pint-loving Lee click with his tea-drinking date Abbi? Can Cameron help politics graduate Joe leave the singles market?

2.title: Episode #11.2
2.plot: 'Cupcake king' Sunny meets fellow self-professed boffin Misha. Twins Rebecca and Stephen nervously embark on dates with engineer Kristian and legal assistant Emily. Fred's dad visits the restaurant.

3.title: Episode #11.3
3.plot: Will the stars align for science-fiction fans Warren and John? Former reality TV star Aisleyne has a list of qualities she is looking for in a man. Surgeon Salam gets a bout a nerves on his date with Tara.

4.title: Episode #11.4
4.plot: Diamond grader Sachen and financial lawyer Priya discover that they've met before. Make-up artist and model Danni meets bar manager Aiden, the tallest man to ever enter the First Dates restaurant.

5.title: Episode #11.5
5.plot: Flirtation turns to faux pas as the drinks flow on songwriter Kristina's date with photographer Nicola. And will cheeky charmer Billy's fear of butter harm his chances with blonde bombshell Olivia?

6.title: Episode #11.6
6.plot: IT worker Rodney is 45 and never had a girlfriend, he meets executive assistant Mandy. Football coach Julian has a date with party animal Becca. Chrissie and Jonny have a sexually charged date.

7.title: Episode #11.7
7.plot: Ruth wants to find a man who can keep up with her in her saucy seventies. Meanwhile, TJ, who's been told that he looks like Johnny Depp, turns up for his date after a few daytime drinks.

8.title: Episode #11.8
8.plot: Helicopter pilot Paul, 59, embarks on his first-ever date dressed in women's clothing will 51-year-old Sydney see he's just a normal bloke. Make up artist and mum of five Bianca meets white van man and single parent Daniel.

9.title: First Dates at Christmas 2018
9.plot: Initially an experiment in which real dates are filmed, and then viewers get the chance to apply to date the unsuccessful participants the following week. Later this aspect was removed and replaced with a cast of regular restaurant staff.

16.title: The Proposal
16.plot: Both returning singles and past successful couples meet up at the First Date restaurant at Christmas time. The title gives away one big "surprise."

1.title: Episode #5.1
1.plot: 'First Dates' is a dating show with a twist that takes advantage of modern forms of dating. Each episode documents a number of couples having dinner in a unique restaurant in which everyone is on a first date. Viewers see the daters from the moment they meet until the meal is over, sharing the highs of lows of each couple's date. At the end of each date, the couple talks candidly about the experience and answers the question everybody has: will the daters see each other again?
